<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>524</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men shì yī zhī wú xíng de jūn lǚ, wǒ men shì wú míng de chuán dào rén,
 shén bāng zhù wǒ men shéi néng dǐ dǎng wǒ men de kǒu hào shì xiàng qián jìn.
 jǐ qiān nián de xùn dào xuè, huàn xǐng le wǒ men zhè hòu lái rén,
 jǐ qiān nián de zhòng shèng tú, chún yī piào liú bù huī xīn.
 zhí dào zhàn chǎng shàng kǎo yàn shì bīng, dà fēng dà làng lǐ kǎo yàn shāo gōng,
 mò hòu de shí dài lǐ gèng kǎo yàn wǒ men, shí shí chù chù qiú zhǔ zhǐ yì.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men shì yī zhī wú xíng de jūn lǚ 迦南524</title>
</song>